<!DOCTYPE html><html ⚡ lang="en"><head> <% include ../_partials/amp/_amp-head.ejs %><script async custom-element="amp-sidebar" src="https://cdn.ampproject.org/v0/amp-sidebar-0.1.js"></script><script async custom-element="amp-accordion" src="https://cdn.ampproject.org/v0/amp-accordion-0.1.js"></script><script async custom-element="amp-form" src="https://cdn.ampproject.org/v0/amp-form-0.1.js"></script><script async custom-element="amp-lightbox" src="https://cdn.ampproject.org/v0/amp-lightbox-0.1.js"></script></head><body class="home"><amp-sidebar id='sidebar' side='right' layout='nodisplay'> <% include ../_partials/amp/_ampLandingSidebar.ejs %></amp-sidebar><header class="header fixed"> <% include ../_partials/amp/_amp-header.ejs %></header><div class="wrap"><div class="container main"> <% include ../_partials/content/_bluenav-usermanual.ejs %><section class="blade wrapper content"><div class="container"><h1 class="post-title">IN-9008 HD User Manual</h1><div class="card-container"><div class="onecard"><div class="image"><a href="/Outdoor_Cameras/IN-9008_HD/Product_Features"><amp-img role="button" tabindex="0" src="/images/Usermanuals/IN-9008_explodedVIew.png" width="842" height="595" layout="responsive"></amp-img></a></div></div><div class="margin"><h2>Download our Print Manual</h2> <a href="/dl/IN-9008HD/QuickInstallation-1080p-IN-9008HD.pdf" target="_blank"><button type="button" name="button" class="btn">PDF Usermanual</button></a></div><div class="card-container"><div class="onecard"><div class="image"><a href="/Outdoor_Cameras/IN-9008_HD/Point2Point"><amp-img role="button" tabindex="0" src="/images/Usermanuals/P2P_Box_5905.psd.png" width="900" height="650" layout="responsive"></amp-img></a><div class="action"><p>Connect your camera to your local WiFi network by just pressing the <button on="tap:reset-button" class="btn btnSmall">WPS Button</button> (WiFi Protected Setup). and access your camera over the internet by scanning the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Network/Remote_Access/">P2P QR Code</a> with our <a href="/Software/iOS/InstarVision/iPhone/P2P">iPhone</a>, <a href="/Software/iOS/InstarVision/iPad/P2P">iPad</a>, <a href="/Software/Android/InstarVision/P2P">Android</a>, <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Windows_Phone/P2P">Windows Phone</a> or <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Metro/P2P">Windows (Metro)</a> App.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="card-container"><div class="twocard"><div class="image"><a href="/Outdoor_Cameras/IN-9008_HD/Lense_Adjustment"><amp-img noloading height=400 width=400 layout=responsive src="/images/Usermanuals/QL-Box_Lense-Adjust_IN-5905HD.png"></amp-img></a></div><div class="action"><h4>Adjust your cameras focal point by simply turning the lense</h4><p class="justify">When you receive your camera, we already adjusted the focus for the camera to be operational in a general surveillance scenario. For outdoor cameras this means, that they give you an sharp image for distances between 5 and 10m. If you need a different focus distance, just open the front of your camera and turn the lense clockwise or counterclockwise, until you have your scene in focus.</p></div></div><div class="twocard"><div class="image"><a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/System/User/"><amp-img noloading height=400 width=400 layout=responsive src="/images/Usermanuals/QL-Box_User_IN-6014HD.png"></amp-img></a></div><div class="action"><h4>Protect your Privacy</h4><p class="justify">Please be aware, that you should change the default login of your camera before you <a href="/Internet_Access/Port_Forwarding/">forward</a> it to the internet.Please <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/System/User/">change the password</a> of <strong>all 3 user classes</strong> - administrator, user and visitor - so that no one can connect to your camera uninvited. If you loose your password, you can always use the <a href="/Outdoor_Cameras/IN-9008_HD/Camera_Reset/">hardware reset</a> of your camera, to go back to the factory defaults.<br><br></p></div></div></div><div class="card-container"><div class="twocard"><div class="image"><a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Alarm/Areas/"><amp-img noloading height=400 width=400 layout=responsive src="/images/Usermanuals/QL-Box_MotionDetection_IN-6014HD.png"></amp-img></a></div><div class="action"><h4>Motion Detection and Video Recording</h4><p class="justify">Use your cameras internal image analysis to efficiently detect people, animals or cars - while moving trees, passign clouds or automatically switched light sources are ignored. Set your camera to start a video or snapshot recording on the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Features/SD_Card/">local SD card</a> and upload those files to an off-site <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Network/FTP/">FTP server</a>.<br><br><br></p></div></div><div class="twocard"><div class="image"><a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Alarm/Actions/"><amp-img noloading height=400 width=400 layout=responsive src="/images/Usermanuals/QL-Box_Notification_IN-6014HD.png"></amp-img></a></div><div class="action"><h4>Email and Push Notification</h4><p class="justify">Set up your camera to use the motion detection function to send you emails or push a notification to your smartphone. <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Alarm/Push_Service/">Push notifications</a> (<a href="/Software/iOS/InstarVision/">iOS</a>, <a href="/Software/Android/InstarVision/">Android</a> and <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Windows_Phone/">Windows Phone</a>) will reach you in an instance. While the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/System/Email/">email notification</a> might take a while, but added the bonus of attached snapshots. Activate both functions to be always informed about what is going on when you are on the road.</p></div></div></div></div></section><amp-lightbox id="reset-button" layout="nodisplay"><div class="lightbox"><div class="card-container"><div class="onecard"><div class="image centered"><amp-img noloading height=596 width=632 layout=fixed src="/images/Usermanuals/IN-9008HD_Camera_Reset.png"></amp-img></div><div class="action"><table class="twelve columns no-highlight"><tr><td><h3 class="inlineHeader">Drücken Sie 3s für WPS oder 15s für Werksreset&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></td><td class="align-right"> <button class="navGo navGoRed" on="tap:reset-button.close">Schließen</button></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div></amp-lightbox></div></div> <% include ../_partials/content/_bluenav-usermanual-mobile.ejs %><footer> <% include ../_partials/amp/_amp-footer.ejs %></footer></body></html>